      "createdAt": "2021-05-17T10:57:57.551Z",
      "author": "kolaai (alfred)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello everyone!<br />\nDuplicates and Uniques is an app by Kolaai which allows you to find any number of duplicate items in your board and perform various actions on them. The app takes you a step by step process to enable you to select the exact kind of items you are interested in. It is built to handle different cases such as:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  Handle large amount of items</li>\n<li>\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  Work on single or multiple groups</li>\n<li>\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  Configure groups to function independently or collectively</li>\n<li>\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  Work on single or multiple columns of different types</li>\n<li>\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  Filter included columns taking in consideration case sensitivity, empty values(both for columns and items)</li>\n<li>\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  Filter the amount and type of data (duplicate or unique) to be returned and also filtering by the item name</li>\n<li>\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  Create status column and label for the found results</li>\n<li>\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  Move or Copy the results to both existing boards or groups, or new boards or groups</li>\n<li>\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  Delete the found results</li>\n<li>\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  Save template and run them as integrations</li>\n<li>\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  Run templates in preferred order</li>\n<li>\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  Work in multiple languages</li>\n<li>\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  And many more…<br />\n<br /><br />\nHandle all your spreadsheet duplicate items right in your Monday board. Duplicate submitted form data can also be handled using saved template integrations. Since any item can either be a duplicate or unique, the possibilities the app offers is limitless! Here is a demo the app in action.<br />\n<div class=\"video-container\">\n    \n      \n      <a href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/e/e9bbea1ff8c272d5da276d26425aec9e03f00c51.mov\">https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/e/e9bbea1ff8c272d5da276d26425aec9e03f00c51.mov</a>\n    \n  </div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We have currently submitted the application to be added to the marketplace but you can click <a href=\"https://auth.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=1ff0c707dfd11339980a5876e9fd15f2&amp;response_type=install\">here</a> to start a 14 days trial right away.  Click <a href=\"https://kolaai.com/\">here</a> to learn about our subscription plans and can reach us at <a href=\"mailto:support@kolaai.com\">support@kolaai.com</a> or using this <a href=\"https://forms.monday.com/forms/f550758c886691f275bcf9c2f139eeca?r=use1\">form</a><br />\n<br /><br />\nHere are some examples of how Duplicates and Uniques can be beneficial.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/0/03a67f34f0e4e223e2de171307fc80ccf58818a9.png\" title=\"Column select (resized)\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/0/03a67f34f0e4e223e2de171307fc80ccf58818a9_2_517x258.png\" alt=\"Column select (resized)\" width=\"517\" height=\"258\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Column select (resized)</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×960 128 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/5/570f22b2bee2e63309ce0b6aaed6d7b6cf628408.jpeg\" title=\"First Step (resized)\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/5/570f22b2bee2e63309ce0b6aaed6d7b6cf628408_2_517x258.jpeg\" alt=\"First Step (resized)\" width=\"517\" height=\"258\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">First Step (resized)</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×960 149 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/8/8c9f2fb2f8b8e75d80433b6c9aef0791bdd87bc4.jpeg\" title=\"Actions_resized\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/8/8c9f2fb2f8b8e75d80433b6c9aef0791bdd87bc4_2_517x258.jpeg\" alt=\"Actions_resized\" width=\"517\" height=\"258\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Actions_resized</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×960 155 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/a/abc3c475a2f4886955f08d7fb6bbcb484076c374.jpeg\" title=\"Integrations (resized)\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/a/abc3c475a2f4886955f08d7fb6bbcb484076c374_2_517x258.jpeg\" alt=\"Integrations (resized)\" width=\"517\" height=\"258\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Integrations (resized)</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×960 225 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>"
