      "createdAt": "2021-07-07T03:16:42.613Z",
      "author": "kolaai (alfred)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>The app has been approved to the marketplace🏆. You can find it <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/130\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">here</a>.<br />\n<br /><br />\n<br /><br />\nIntroducing Merge Duplicates <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tada.png?v=12\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />!!!<br />\n<br /><br />\n<img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/f/f6779ca600a2cb5399b26698940c60e976cd99a7.png\" alt=\"OptionsMerge\" width=\"245\" height=\"398\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> You can merge Duplicates including or excluding the first instance.<br />\n<br /><br />\n<img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/c/c037737db90e88af7fd908996603b92e4f505795.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"436\" height=\"148\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> You can merge automatically:<br />\n<img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/9/91ab99915b336e8877a1c6dd9333e54b4308ea69.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"399\" height=\"276\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Or manually.<br />\nWith manual merge, you have the option to select which values should be used, create new values, join values or even calculate new values<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/a/af6627078b7b5bdd41c70a4481b1e8506679baaa.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/a/af6627078b7b5bdd41c70a4481b1e8506679baaa_2_690x287.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"287\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1229×512 16.8 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/2/2730b921cfabf1ea0758bd853171b2df31ed568f.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/2/2730b921cfabf1ea0758bd853171b2df31ed568f_2_690x281.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"281\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1239×505 11.6 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/0/0ffb23b04811b16460bebd2521b5a9cf7f7452a9.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/0/0ffb23b04811b16460bebd2521b5a9cf7f7452a9_2_690x299.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"299\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1213×526 11.7 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/2/2d8462d00fc635714cf88fcb56d6df5827222e36.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/2/2d8462d00fc635714cf88fcb56d6df5827222e36.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"689\" height=\"227\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1231×405 8.55 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/b/b5cf7d9c1ffc94b277ba0025eacfb791211585d4.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/b/b5cf7d9c1ffc94b277ba0025eacfb791211585d4_2_690x416.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"416\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1222×737 26.2 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/b/be274eb2cac6d156ed1bcf8bcbfe0526bfa0ba67.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/b/be274eb2cac6d156ed1bcf8bcbfe0526bfa0ba67_2_690x364.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"364\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1232×651 15.6 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<br />\nAnd so much more!!!\nTry it now."
