      "author": "kolaai (alfred)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/katecan\">@KateCan</a>,</p>\n<p>Yes, you can use the app for that and can even do it automatically using integrations. Here is a <a href=\"https://www.loom.com/share/cb781a08d1314f08af53dd894d7b1b6a\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">demo</a> of how it works. If you need any help, you can always write to <a href=\"mailto:support@kolaai.com\">support@kolaai.com</a> and we will be happy to help you. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>"
