      "id": 81100,
      "postNumber": 5,
      "createdAt": "2022-03-28T04:04:39.754Z",
      "author": "kolaai (alfred)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Cross-Board support is here!!! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tada.png?v=12\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/trophy.png?v=12\" title=\":trophy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":trophy:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/9/91bba0a42b93760e91b622784934e2fd351a747a.gif\" alt=\"dance-emoji\" width=\"498\" height=\"498\" class=\"animated\" /></p>\n<p>You can now find duplicates and unique items across different boards automatically!<br />\nHere is an example of how</p>          \n            \n          \n<p>\nAs always, if you have any questions, you can always reach out at <a href=\"mailto:support@kolaai.com\">support@kolaai.com</a></p>"
