    {
      "id": 90447,
      "postNumber": 6,
      "createdAt": "2022-07-05T15:10:37.347Z",
      "author": "kolaai (alfred)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p><a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/130\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Duplicates and Uniques</a> now supports Sub-items!! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tada.png?v=12\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/clap.png?v=12\" title=\":clap:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":clap:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tada.png?v=12\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>What this means is that, you can now</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Find duplicates and uniques in sub-items</li>\n<li>Find duplicates and uniques in sub-items together with regular items</li>\n<li>Find duplicates and uniques in sub-items in different boards or with different parent items</li>\n<li>Merge sub-items</li>\n<li>Move form response to sub-items</li>\n<li>Create sub-item templates and so much more…!!!</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Download the app from the <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/130\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">marketplace</a> and explore the limitless possibilities <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/ok_hand.png?v=12\" title=\":ok_hand:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":ok_hand:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 105556,
      "postNumber": 7,
      "createdAt": "2022-11-29T12:42:52.353Z",
      "author": "kolaai (alfred)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p><a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/130\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Duplicates and Uniques</a> now supports “<strong>OR</strong>” operations!!! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tada.png?v=12\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/blush.png?v=12\" title=\":blush:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":blush:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>You can now find duplicates or unique values in either of the selected columns.</p>\n<p>For example, finding a duplicate client either by phone number or email address.<br />\nThe “<strong>OR</strong>” option can be enabled by checking the “Match at least one” checkbox in Step 2</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/3/38f426b111d275eb83e390e41b852e76634e42a2.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/3/38f426b111d275eb83e390e41b852e76634e42a2_2_690x343.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"343\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1870×932 48.1 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>If you need any help with the app, you can always reach out at <a href=\"mailto:support@kolaai.com\">support@kolaai.com</a></p>"
    }
